Did you know that America will lead the world stage in end-time events? Are you interested in learning about the subtle tactics Satan will use to deceive the entire world? Join Truth Matters, a thought-provoking series featuring Matthew Schanche and MacKenzie Drebit. Together, they dive deep into Bible prophecy and current events, offering a vital word of warning to the world through Christian eyes.

In this episode, unravel the identities of the dragon, the beast, and the false prophet in Revelation, and their connection to Project 2025. Explore how America's pursuit of uniting church and state aligns with Bible prophecy and the mark of the beast. Discover why religious think tanks aim to bring back “traditional” values and how that may pose a threat to Christians. Did you know the Bible predicts strong right-wing politics right before the coming of Christ?
Don't miss this series! Join this eye-opening journey with Truth Matters. Your understanding of the world will be forever transformed!
